snippet.title: Widelands Build 20
snippet.description:
Showcase of the new features in Widelands Build 20. Widelands is a free, open source real-time buildup strategy game with single player campaigns and a multiplayer mode. Get it at https://wl.widelands.org/wiki/Download/

This video was created with free software:

Open Broadcaster Software
https://obsproject.com/

https://shotcut.org/

https://www.gimp.org/
